messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Enemy communication intercepted. Security level elevated.

A summary has been copied and printed to all communications consoles.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Hip-hop into Easter!

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: We here at Central Command are testing our new voice teleportation program. Please state a location and an object for us to test with.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: The test has been concluded.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Did it work, Captain?

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: I guess the technology works perfectly, anyone may now request important teleports over general comms now.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

Pyroclastic anomaly detected on long range scanners. Expected location: Aft Maintenance.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: How goes the expiremental teleporter so far?

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Did any of you order Corgis?

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Exterminate them immediately.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: All personnel, destroy the corgi menace immediately.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Failure to destroy the corgis can result in termination of your contract. These corgis are a dangerous anomaly. If left to spread, we all will die.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Station Report. Are the Corgis dead?

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Oh god. They've taken Central Command. KILL THEM ALL!

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: We have taken control of this station. Submit at once.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Once the ritual is complete, the corgi king shall rain death on you all.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Fools, we control NanoTrasen now. You are the only pocket of resistance.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: We demand the Command of this station as sacrafice. Head to the mining station, and only you shall perish. Otherwise, the Corgi King shall slay all.

messages.author: Captain's Announcement
messages.body: Only if you pinkie promise.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: We don't have pinkies, we're fucking corgis mate.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Wait. Card the AI and give him to the Corgi Priest.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: He can live, but his power may be used for resistance.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: He is attacking our men.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Electrical Storm Alert

An electrical storm has been detected in your area, please repair potential electronic overloads.

messages.author: Captain's Announcement
messages.body: COR-R-RG-GI GODSSS M-MUSSST-T-T B-B-BE PL-LEASSS-SSSE!!

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Are commands are not met.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Hurry, the Corgi King is almost amongst us.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: What do you propose?

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Very well. HoS remain where you are. Servant, finish the preparations.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Servant, you must hurry, before the shuttle arrives. The Corgi King is ready, my friend.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: IT HAS BEGUN. RUN MY SERVANT, TO THE SHUTTLE.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: The Corgi Kings have arrived.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: The HoS has fled and left you all to die. The Corgi King awaits him at CentComm.
